Package cycleguard.database.rides

Class ProcessRideService

java.lang.Object
cycleguard.database.rides.ProcessRideService
@Service public class ProcessRideService extends Object
Service wrapper for processing a new submitted ride. Call processNewRide(java.lang.String, cycleguard.database.rides.ProcessRideService.RideInfo) to fully process a new ride, updating every related database entry.
